Package Control Messages
========================

SublimeLinter
-------------

  SublimeLinter 4.6
  =================
  
  You can now set "lint_mode" per linter.
  
  If you have "background" as your default mode, this new setting allows you
  to run some linters only on save, or manually.
  
  http://www.sublimelinter.com/en/stable/linter_settings.html
